        <div class="chapter" data-narrate="true">
            <div class="chapter-title">üîß CHAPTER ONE: The Operation</div>
            <p>Brer Sheep opened an "auto salvage yard" that specialized in tractor parts. The problem? The tractors weren't salvaged. They were stolen.</p>
            <p>Every night, Brer Sheep and Brer Raccoon would drive around stealing tractors from farms, bring them to the chop shop, dismantle them, and sell the parts online with "no questions asked" pricing.</p>
            <div class="dialogue">
                <span class="character">Brer Raccoon</span>: "Where'd you get this John Deere engine?"<br><br>
                <span class="character">Brer Sheep</span>: "Found it."<br><br>
                <span class="character">Brer Raccoon</span>: "Found it WHERE?"<br><br>
                <span class="character">Brer Sheep</span>: "...attached to a tractor... in someone's barn... that we borrowed permanently."
            </div>
